<UIForeground>F201FC</UIForeground><UIGlow>F201FD</UIGlow> Quest Sync<UIGlow>01</UIGlow><UIForeground>01</UIForeground>
Liinel Ja would like to ask a favor of you.
Search for and obtain Jayunja butterflies.
Deliver the Jayunja butterflies to Liinel Ja.
Oh, how fortuitous that we should meet! For you, who have heralded the winds of change for all Mamook, I have a favor to ask.
There are butterflies near Cenote Jayunja that glow a soft blue. Not the giant beasts, but rather small flittering creatures. Swift and clever.
Catching them may prove more taxing than you anticipate, but I would be eternally grateful if you could bring me three.
Would you be so kind as to catch me three butterflies from Cenote Jayunja? The small ones, mind─not the larger beasts.
Were you able to find the butterflies?
The very ones! We release a flutter of these during the exchange of matrimonial vows, to celebrate a couple's new journey together.
Cenote Jayunja in particular is regarded as sacred. The butterflies that live there are thus prized above all for such ceremonies.
They say the contrasting wings, when pressed together in rest, embody the joining of two lovers from different clans, and the everlasting devotion between them.
No symbol could be more auspicious, especially when delivered by the hands that have borne new possibility to our city.
You and the Third Promise have done more for us than you will ever know. These butterflies are sure to bring every happiness to the couple they bless.
